reviews.customers_say: Customers find the wedding dress to be well-made, comfortable, and flattering, with one mentioning it accommodates a size G bust.

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Wedding dress finds!
items.body: I was skeptical about ordering this dress, but it’s really cute. The lace doesn’t feel cheap and the back is really nice. The only thing is the bra portion is see through but once you put it on, it blends in. Also the sleeves are a little tight, so if you have larger arms be mindful about that other than that the dress is really cute and doesn’t feel cheap at all!!! 5/5 Read more
items.author: Veronica Herrera

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars GET THE DRESS!!
items.body: BEAUTIFUL. Weird that it has tan padding in a lace top and you can see them thru it but it blended well in my pictures. I loved this. It fit perfect. Zipper on the back. Im 5’5 & 165lbs and it fit me perfect. Sleeves were the perfect length. Bust fit great. I taped my girls up no bra. Used shapewear shorts. Made my figure look great. GREAT Quality. No smell on arrival. Very comfortable to sit down in. Read more
items.author: Emily

items.title: 4.0 out of 5 stars Can’t believe the quality!
items.body: I bought SEVERAL dresses and tried on all price ranges and landed with this. I have no regrets. I had the cups replaced with white ones. I actually washed the dress after in the washing machine and hung to dry and it still looks brand new. Don’t hesitate to buy! ♥️ Read more
items.author: Vanessa_Mae

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Fantastic Choice
items.body: I got this for a low-key wedding last-minute after a custom ordered gown from Amazon was executed well but didn’t feel right for my bust. This came within a day and was so surprised. It holds up my size G bust, doesn’t show any belly issues, and has a very beautiful back. I did choose to not have it be overly fitting with an xxl, helping me accommodate my chest while not being form fitting on my stomach or hips. The only potential con is the little cups do have a neutral look through a pretty sheer top. I’m okay with that and also considering seeing if I can get a seamstress to switch out the cups for a bigger size. If I had to go with it as is today, I’d be really content. Read more
items.author: Hibiscus

items.title: 1.0 out of 5 stars No me gustó
items.body: La parte de los senos es muy amarillo y el vestido es blanco deberían solucionarlo Read more
items.author: Altagracia n.

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Well worth it!
items.body: Dress fit perfectly! WOW the price, the way it felt, what a steal!!! Read more
items.author: Jessica Rae

items.title: 3.0 out of 5 stars Tight sleeves.
items.body: Sleeves were extremely tight. The rest of the dress was nice. There is no smell and it seemed soft and comfortable. But I don’t have particularly large arms and I could not get my arms in. Read more
items.author: Meg P.

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Gorgeous dress
items.body: Beautiful dress, I wore this on my elopement and everyone thought it was a really expensive dress. I did have it altered and replaced the yellow cups with some nude looking ones my seamstress had, it made an entire difference. I would recommend getting it altered to you. Great quality. Read more
items.author: Michelle

short_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve Mermaid is made for a polished look that still feels comfortable to wear. It is designed to sit cleanly on the body with a flattering shape that works for day plans and dressier moments without feeling overdone.

The fit focuses on balance rather than extremes, so you can move naturally while still getting a defined silhouette. Choose your usual size for a closer look, or size up if you prefer a little more ease through the waist and hips.

Styling is simple: keep accessories minimal for a clean finish, or add a jacket and statement shoes when you want a sharper outfit. This piece photographs well thanks to smooth lines and a structured feel that stays put once you have it adjusted.

With the right fit and simple styling, this item becomes an easy go-to when you want something that looks intentional without requiring extra effort.

To keep it looking sharp, follow the care label first and avoid high heat when drying or steaming if the material is sensitive.

The design is easy to style with simple accessories and works well in photos thanks to clean lines and a balanced silhouette.

long_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve Mermaid is a versatile piece you can reach for when you want a put-together look that still feels comfortable. The goal is simple: a silhouette that reads polished, photographs well, and stays wearable for a full day or a long night.

Fit and sizing Fit is where most outfits win or lose. This design aims for a balanced shape with a defined line through the torso, a clean waist, and a smooth finish through the hips and legs. If you prefer a more relaxed feel, size up; if you like a closer fit, stay true to size. Sizes may include: XS, S, M, L, XL.

Fabric and comfort Comfort is not just about softness. It is also about movement and how the fabric behaves as you walk, sit, and stand. A fabric blend with a bit of give helps it keep its shape while still feeling wearable.

Highlights A clean neckline and a refined silhouette for an elevated look. Designed to layer easily with jackets, wraps, or sweaters. Works well with both minimal accessories and statement pieces.

How to style Styling ideas: keep it minimal with neutral shoes and one standout accessory. For a relaxed daytime look, add a denim jacket or cardigan. For events, switch to a bolder shoe and a small clutch for a sharper finish.

Color notes Available colors may include: White. If a shade is sold out, check back as availability can change.

Care Care guidance matters if you want it to keep its shape and finish. Follow the label first.
